Posts.Content: Hi! I'm a Stage II Breast Cancer survivor in my mid-twenites living in New York.  I'm also a writer and an actor.  While I was undergoing chemotherapy last year, I began a vlog chronicling my experience and my journey to health.  My website is: www.ThatTimeIHadCancer.com It's humorous, but always honest, and I like to think informative.  I hope you check it out and find things you relate to.
Posts.Title: Cancer Vlog
